:name: XIAO nRF52840 + simulated PMW3610 trackball
:description: Boot this module's ZMK image with a PMW3610 simulation on SPIM0; console on uart0, Studio RPC on uart1.

# Same layout as zmk-west-commands' scripts/lib/renode/platforms/single.resc
# (console on uart0, Studio RPC on uart1, no `start` -- the harness starts
# the emulation after it has connected to both UART sockets), plus:
#   - compiles the PMW3610 sensor simulation (PMW3610.cs) before loading
#     the platform description that instantiates it
#   - loads the local xiao_pmw3610.repl (SPIM0 + trackball + CS/IRQ wiring)

using sysbus

$bin?=@zmk.elf
$console_port?=3455
$rpc_port?=3456

include @platforms/PMW3610.cs
include @platforms/NRF52840_GPIO_WithLatch.cs

mach create "pmw3610"
machine LoadPlatformDescription @platforms/xiao_pmw3610.repl

emulation CreateServerSocketTerminal $console_port "console_term" false
connector Connect sysbus.uart0 console_term

emulation CreateServerSocketTerminal $rpc_port "rpc_term" false
connector Connect sysbus.uart1 rpc_term

sysbus LoadELF $bin
